{"title":"登花塔观潮","authors":["刘丙辰"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":12,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"登花塔观潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘丙辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着苏轼攀登的石梯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过古榕参天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花塔清风依旧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒸蒸市容扑面而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泱泱流花湖成了梳妆的镜子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔珠江宛如腰间飘曳的碧带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着鳞次栉比的高厦向着云层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩虹飞架，立交桥正将羊城的气度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煊然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在花塔之巅向人海俯瞰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默读古往今来的变幻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下古刹，千佛竞辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座花城，以跨世纪的风采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装饰着珠江两岸"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}